    <h1>Proximity Factor</h1>
    <p class="description">One of Google's three core local ranking signals — the geographic distance between a searcher and your business. Closer businesses rank higher by default; understanding the proximity factor is the first step to overcoming it.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
