            </button>
            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The Vicinity Update (November 2021) significantly increased proximity's weight. Sterling Sky documented major ranking shifts where businesses closer to the searcher displaced higher-profile competitors. If your local rankings dropped in late 2021, proximity displacement was likely the cause.</p></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
